---
title: Saigon-Style Steaks with Tomato Rice and Cilantro-Lime Greens
description: This Vietnamese-inspired beef recipe really sizzles—seriously! You'll love the sweet and salty sauce gently spiced with sweet chili heat, and the whole plate is rounded out with tomato rice and a refreshing, tangy salad.

